### 3. Quick Ratio

- Inventory = 7,832,820.00
- Quick Assets (Current Assets - Inventory) = 13,753,616.13 - 7,832,820.00 = 5,920,796.13

Quick Ratio = 5,920,796.13 รท 5,515,978.61 = 1.07
